---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>🚁 Aerial Storytelling & Drone Media</h1>
			<p>
				Welcome to UNIQM, your partner for premium aerial photography and videography in real estate. Based in the Netherlands, we specialize in capturing stunning drone footage that brings properties to life.
			</p>
			<p>
				Our expertise includes high-quality aerial perspectives, immersive property showcases, and compelling visual narratives that help real estate agents and developers present their properties in the best possible light.
			</p>
			<p>What we offer:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Professional aerial photography and videography</li>
				<li>Real estate property showcases</li>
				<li>Drone cinematography and visual storytelling</li>
				<li>Post-production editing and enhancement</li>
				<li>360-degree property views and virtual tours</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Whether you're a real estate agent, developer, or property owner in the Netherlands, UNIQM delivers exceptional aerial content that stands out. Let us help you tell your property's story from the skies.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
